# yaml2env

## How to use

export $(yaml2env config.yaml)

## Example format of a yaml file
```yaml
---
env:

  API_PORT: 5001
  API_HOST: 127.0.0.1
  PROJECT_NAME: 'test project'
  IMAGE_BASE_URL: 'https://example.com/'

``` 


